quote_last: Greet Priscilla and Aquila and the household of Onesiphorus.
title: 2 Timothy
author: NIV

quote_last: The great city was split into three parts, and the cities of the nations fell, and God remembered Babylon the great, to make her drain the cup of the wine of the fury of his wrath.
title: Revelation
author: ESV

quote_last: The churches in the province of Asia send you greetings. Aquila and Priscilla greet you warmly in the Lord, and so does the church that meets at their house.
title: 1 Corinthians
author: NIV
